cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and modeling of review text. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses recurrent point processes for modeling. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with recommendation systems. The paper also discusses seasonal effects, which could place it under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) if the reviews are related to music or audio.
